### Log in
### Ping
GET http://localhost:8080/api/ping

### Register
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Me
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/me

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout

############################################################################################
### Comments
### 1. Get comments for anime id 1
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/1/comments

### 2. Try posting a comment without login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/anime/1/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This anime is amazing!"
}

### 3. Login first
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "demo",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. Get current logged-in user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/me

### 5. Post a comment after login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/anime/1/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This anime is amazing!"
}

### 6. Get comments again
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/1/comments

############################################################################################
### Watch List
### 1. Log in first
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "demo",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Get current user watch list
GET http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist

### 3. Get one watch list entry
GET http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist/1

### 4. Add a new anime to watch list
POST http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "animeId": 2,
  "status": "WATCH_LATER",
  "personalRating": 7
}

### 5. Update watch list entry
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "personalRating": 9
}

### 6. Delete watch list entry
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist/2

### 7. Verify the global rating really changed
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/2

############################################################################################
### Error Handling
### 1. Validation error on register
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "email": "wrong-email",
  "password": "123"
}

### 2. Validation error on watch list rating
POST http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: JSESSIONID=your-session-id

{
  "animeId": 1,
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "personalRating": 15
}

### 3. Anime not found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/99999

### 4. Unauthorized watch list access
GET http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist

### 5. Duplicate register

### 6. Invalid login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "demo",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}